1
00:00:00,050 --> 00:00:04,150
The named field operates downstream of where BiRAGAS plays.

2
00:00:04,150 --> 00:00:06,800
Recursion runs phenomic screens.

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:09,550
Insilico runs generative chemistry.

4
00:00:09,550 --> 00:00:14,800
Schrödinger runs molecular simulation — all on already-chosen targets.

5
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:19,787
BenevolentAI runs associative knowledge graphs without mechanistic validation.

6
00:00:19,787 --> 00:00:25,225
Tempus and Foundation Medicine, including Roche, scale correlation-based clinical genomics.

7
00:00:25,225 --> 00:00:31,437
OpenAI and DeepMind run biomedical association prediction with no regulatory architecture.

8
00:00:31,437 --> 00:00:35,300
The top five players hold just under twelve percent of the market.

9
00:00:35,300 --> 00:00:39,362
No dominant platform exists at the layer BiRAGAS occupies.

